data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home located in the highly sought after Copper Creek Community! This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home features an open concept layout, adorned with modern upgraded finishes that you and/or family will love. Relax in your luxurious master suite which includes a complete upgraded Galleria closet as well as an ensuite bathroom. This incredible property offers the perfect backyard with plenty of space, which is perfect for entertaining your family and friends. Enjoy the screened-in back patio and fenced backyard which sets this home apart from the rest. This home is one of a kind, and it will not last long!
